Author: Herculezz, James, erdelf
Name: AutoDuty
Description: A plugin to run dungeons for you with Trust, Duty Support, Squadrons, Variants, and Regular, Requires BossMod, vnavmesh and a Rotation Plugin (BossMod AutoRotation, Wrath or RotationSolverReborn)
Changelog:
## What's Changed
* fix build tab context loosing by @erdelf in https://github.com/ffxivcode/AutoDuty/pull/717
* Xelphatol path update by @erdelf in https://github.com/ffxivcode/AutoDuty/pull/718
* Wrath IPC: Proper callback and new setting added by @erdelf in https://github.com/ffxivcode/AutoDuty/pull/721
* BMR range check before set by @erdelf in https://github.com/ffxivcode/AutoDuty/pull/722
* Overlay not closed via Escape by @erdelf in https://github.com/ffxivcode/AutoDuty/pull/724
* default wrath non tank targeting changed by @erdelf in https://github.com/ffxivcode/AutoDuty/pull/725
* Pharos Sirius interaction update by @erdelf in https://github.com/ffxivcode/AutoDuty/pull/728

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/ffxivcode/AutoDuty/compare/0.0.0.181...0.0.0.182
